values:
this break has been okay.
today was the first day i didn't do "something/anything" but it's cool.
hm, i think livejournal has very less people than i thought it did. no one added me back on my old friends list.
no one likes livejournal. : [ saddd.
okay, well im pretty sure im off to do some cleaning because im wide awake and no one is online [its 1:30 exactly am.]
i woke up at 3 today to my sister calling. lovely.
okay, have a wonderful break guys/girls. and yay, 3 more days until christmas.

errors in last entry.
im computer challenged, and can not seem to fix it.

For some much needed fun.

I love my trips home from the bus stop.

And, I now have a small passion for ice skating.

And, finally my Saturday was splendid with my lovely best friends.

Finally, the FLG's minus two, who couldn't make it.
not only do i want to spend this holiday break happy. but i want to spend the rest of my life happy.

i love finding out random facts about people.
some are disturbing, but others... simply make me think.
hmm...

Dear God,

Make me a bird, so I can fly far; far, far away from here.

"holy crap today has been the most useless and pointless day
accomplished nothing.... nothing important that is." -h.g.

but yeah, that sums up my life. : ]
and i got a new sn. if you want it, ask me. cause some faggs keep i-ming that i dont know. hate it.

<s>im officially back to livejournal. </s>
or im trying it out at least.
hm. yep.
